@ontos 1.0
@title AI handoff example
@type ai-handoff
@updated 2026-06-05

- Parser task @id(parser-task) #task #ai
  context: Implement the reference parser for .ontos Format 1.0.
  boundary:
    - Work inside packages/parser.
    - Preserve public API names.
  do_not_touch:
    - Do not rename ontosfmt.
    - Do not change @ontos-protocol package scope.
  acceptance:
    - Valid conformance fixtures parse successfully.
    - Invalid conformance fixtures produce expected diagnostics.
  verify:
    - Run parser unit tests.
    - Run schema validation against AST snapshots.
  handoff: Continue with formatter once parser fixtures pass.
